Weather apps are essential tools that everyone uses to plan their day or week.By building one, you’ll see how Python can solve real problems and create usefultools.
Tools Used :-
  •Python: You’ve been learning it, and now you’ll see how powerful it canbe!
  •Visual Studio Code (VS Code): An easy-to-use code editor where wecan write and test our Python code.
  •OpenWeatherMap API: A free service that provides real-time weatherdata
